sagex.phoenix.util

Class Hints

  • java.lang.Object
    • sagex.phoenix.util.Hints
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Hints
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Hints are named data elements that can be passed around that may understood by the receiver.

    for example, A Search() method may take Hints to affect the search. Or an Update() method may accept Hints to affect how data is Updated()
